<h1>Configure your database</h1>

<p>Gatekeeper stores its configuration in a PostgreSQL database. You can either choose the built-in server or configure a custom one.</p>

<div class="form-check">
    <input type="checkbox" class="form-check-input">
    <label class="form-check-label">Built-in Database<br />Use the built-in PostgreSQL database.</label>
</div>

<div class="form-check">
    <input type="checkbox" class="form-check-input">
    <label class="form-check-label">Configure custom database<br />Use your own PostgreSQL database.</label>
</div>
